","text":" "},{"text":"Init and retain an instance with the Source or PaymentIntent you want to handle,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then choose a redirect method. The context will fire the completion handler"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when the redirect completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Due to the nature of iOS, very little concrete information can be gained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"during this process, as all actions take place in either the Safari app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or the sandboxed SFSafariViewController class. The context attempts to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detect when the user has completed the necessary redirect action by listening"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for both app foregrounds and url callbacks received in the app delegate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"However, it is possible the when the redirect is “completed”, the user may","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have not actually completed the necessary actions to authorize the charge."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You should not use either this class, nor "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"STPAPIClient"},{"text":", as a way","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to determine when you should charge the Source or to determine if the redirect"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was successful. Use Stripe webhooks on your backend server to listen for Source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"state changes and to make the charge.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPRedirectContext","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"STPRedirectContext","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"STPRedirectContext","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},